根據[[美國人口普查局|美國人口普查局]]的統計，奧本山市總面積為{{convert|16.64|sqmi|sqkm|2}}。其中{{convert|16.60|sqmi|sqkm|2}}的陸域和 {{convert|0.04|sqmi|sqkm|2}} 的水域。<ref name ="Gazetteer files">{{cite web|title=US Gazetteer files 2010|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|publisher=[[United_States_Census_Bureau|United States Census Bureau]]|accessdate=2012-11-25|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/699nOulzi?url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|archive-date=2012-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

